Hi, I'm Khadine!

I'm a UI Designer based in Los Angeles, CA.

With a background in Fine Arts, I focus on creating empathic user-centric experiences and visually stunning UI Designs. I have a passion for visual design and a knack for solving problems.

Trail Goods

Trail Goods is a plant-adventure hiking app developed for iOS and Android. It acts as a tool for hikers and nature enthusiasts to learn about plants and fungi, all while out on a trail.

Cooking 101

Cooking 101 is a responsive web app for college students looking to expand their culinary palettes.

For this project, it was important that I kept a mobile first approach.

The Print Shop

The Print Shop is a user-friendly responsive web app that offers a wide range of tools and supplies for Printmakers of all skill levels.

Whether you're an expert or just someone looking for a gift for a creative friend, this e-commerce site is designed to be fun and easy to navigate.
